= Include Module

The include module allows you to include content from other files.

== Basic Include

include::example-file.remarkd[]

== Include with Attributes

include::example-file.remarkd[lines=1..10]

== Include Examples

include::header.remarkd[]

include::footer.remarkd[]

== Include in Sections

== Included Content

include::content-section.remarkd[]

== Include with Formatting

This paragraph introduces included content:

include::example.remarkd[]

