== Include with Conditional Content

ifeval::[version >= 2.0]
include::new-features.remarkd[]
endif::[]

== Include Module Usage

The include module is useful for:

* Reusing common content
* Organizing large documents
* Maintaining consistency

include::common-content.remarkd[]

